longBusinessSummary: Swaraj Engines Limited manufactures and sells diesel engines and its engine components, hi-tech engine, and spare parts for tractors in India. The company was incorporated in 1985 and is based in Mohali, India. Swaraj Engines Limited is a subsidiary of Mahindra & Mahindra Limited.
